                                                  bǝrhān</title>
                      </msItem>
                    </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="138v" to="139v" facs="143">Fols 138v–139v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3108RepCh388">Yǝweddǝsǝwwa
                                                  malāʾǝkt la-Māryām</title></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="140r" to="140v" facs="144">Fols 140r–140v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3100RepCh380">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Giyorgis</title>
                    <note>Starts at the second stanza</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      ኦ[፡] ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡ ለጽኑዕ፡ ወለድኩም፡<lb/>
                      ወለነፍሰ፡ ኵሉ፡ ቃውም።<lb/>
                      ጊዮርጊስ፡ የዋህ፡ እንበለ፡ መስፈርት፡ ወአቅም።<lb/>
                      ከመ፡ እግዝእትከ፡ ቡርክት፡ ማርያም፡<lb/>
                      ርኅሩኃ፡ ልብ፡ አንተ፡ እምበቀል፡ ወቂም።
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="141r" to="141v" facs="145">Fols 141r–141v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2915RepCh196">Malkǝʾ-hymn to
                                                  Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለስንሠትከ፡ መሰረተ፡ ነገር፡ ወውጣኔ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ ሰላም፡<lb/>
                    በብስራተ፡ መልAክ፡ ሠናየ፡ ቅኔ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                 <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="142r" to="143v" facs="146">Fols 142r–143v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3082RepCh362">Hymn to Our Lady
                                                  Mary</title>
                  <incipit>
                    <gap reason="omitted"/>
                    ሰላም፡ ለአዕንትኪ፡ Aምሳለ፡ ፪ቱ፡ ቀናዲል። እንተ፡ ሰቀሎን፡<lb/>
                    ኬንያ፡ በማሕፈደ፡ ሥጋ፡ ልሁል።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6"><locus from="144r" to="145v" facs="148">Fols 144r–145v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2866RepCh147">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7"><locus from="146r" to="147v" facs="150">Fols 146r–147v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3085RepCh365">Hymn to Raguel the
                                                  Archangel</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለመልክዕከ፡ ለለ፩፩ዱ።<lb/>
                    ዘበበስሙ፡ ወበበ፡ መፍቅዱ።<lb/>
                    ራጉኤል፡ ኀቤከ፡ ሶበ፡ ያንቀዓዱ።<lb/>
                    ተወከፍ፡ ስእለተ፡ ገብርከ፡ ለፈጽሞ፡ ኵሉ፡ ፈቃዱ።<lb/>
                    ከመ፡ ይትዌከፍ፡ Aብ፡ ስእለቶ፡ ለወልዱ፡
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="147v" to="147v" facs="152">Fols 147v–147v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2846RepCh129">Malkǝʾ-hymn to the
                                                  angel Uriel</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ በAፈ፡ ኵሉ፡ ጥዑም፡<lb/>
                    ለዘይጼውዖ፡ ረዳኢ፡ እንበለ፡ መስፈርት፡ ወዓቅም።<lb/>
                    ሩፋኤል፡ መልAክ፡ ዖፈ፡ አርያም።<lb/>
                    ታሕተ፡ ወግር፡ ከመ፡ ሰወርከ፡ ለመልAከ፡ ሐከክ፡ ዘቅድም።<lb/>
                    ለደቂቀ፡ ስሕተት፡ ዘደም፡ ሠውሮሙ፡ ዮም።<lb/>
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9"><locus from="148r" to="149v" facs="152">Fols 148r–149v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ሐዋዝ።<lb/>
                    እምነ፡ ከልበኔ፡ ወቍስጥ፡ ወእምነ፡ ሰንበልት፡ ምዑዝ።<lb/>
                    ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ለባሲተ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ትእዛዝ።<lb/>
                    ይስቅየኒ፡ ለለጽባሁ፡ ወይነ፡ ፍቅርኪ፡ አዚዝ፡<lb/>
                    ከመ፡ ይሰቅዮ፡ ውሂዝ፡ ለሠናይ፡ ዓርዝ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10"><locus from="150r" to="151v" facs="154">Fols 150r–151v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4131Salam">Salām to Jesus
                                                  Christ</title>
                  <note>Folio missing between <locus target="#150v #151r" facs="155">fols. 150v, 151r</locus></note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11"><locus from="152r" to="153v" facs="156">Fols 152r–153v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12"><locus from="154r" to="154v" facs="158">Fols 154r–154v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2930RepCh211">Malkǝʾa ʾAbuna
                                                  Takla Hāymānot</title>
                  <note>Excerpt</note>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ስብሐት፡ ይደሉ፡ ለማርያም፡ በሰጊድ፡ ወAስተሐምሞ።<lb/>
                    ዘከፈለተኒ፡ ቃለ፡ አወድሰከ፡ በኢያርምሞ።<lb/>
                    ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ግበር፡ ለልብየ፡ ዘይኤድሞ፡<lb/>
                    እስመ፡ ነገርኩ፡ ለመልክዕከ፡ ሰላሞ።<lb/>
                    ግብረ፡ ዘወሀብከኒ፡ ፈጸምኩ፡ ፈጽሞ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i13"><locus from="155r" to="155v" facs="159">Fols 155r–155v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2883RepCh164">Malkǝʾa madḫāne
                                                  ʿālam</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘኢረከቡ፡ ተፍጻሜተ።<lb/>
                    መላEክተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ወምድር፡ እለ፡ ለመዱ፡ ስብሐተ፡<lb/>
                    መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡ ተወከፍ፡ እንተ፡ አቅረብኩ፡ ንስቲተ።<lb/>
                    ዘሰተይከ፡ በእንቲAየ፡ ከርቤ፡ ወሐሞተ።<lb/>
                    በሞተ፡ ዚAከ፡ ከመ፡ ትቅትል፡ ሞተ።
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i14"><locus from="156r" to="159v" facs="160">Fols 156r–159v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2246salotz">Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾǝtǝna
                                                  Māryām ba-Dabra Golgotā</title>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i15"><locus from="160r" to="163v" facs="164">Fols 160r–163v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2807RepCh91">Malkǝʾ-hymn to Our
                                                  Lady Mary</title>
                  <note>Excerpt containing the sections for matins, compline and midnight.</note>
                </msItem>
